30:43.800 --> 30:44.320
Zhuangzhuang

30:56.080 --> 30:56.580
Zhuangzhuang

30:59.660 --> 31:00.180
Entschuldigung

31:03.420 --> 31:04.360
Damals

31:04.880 --> 31:06.580
